headline: Agoda reveals trending Asian destinations for Lunar New Year travel, Tokyo retains the top spot
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has unveiled the top destinations in Asia for the upcoming Lunar New Year, based on accommodation search data. Tokyo (Japan), retains its top position, followed by Bangkok (Thailand), and Taipei (Taiwan) making to the top three for the first time.
